Usage: app_name tag (-h|--help)
       app_name tag [options] <tag_name> [filtering options|<note_name>...]
       app_name tag [options] --remove-all [filtering options|<note_name>...]

Options:
{% include default_options_help %}
  --remove              Remove a tag from the requested notes.
  --remove-all          Remove all tags from the requested notes.

